## Certificate Management

### Certificate Installation
```bash
# Install BearDog commercial certificate
nestgate-cli cert install --type commercial --file beardog-commercial.cert

# Verify certificate status
nestgate-cli cert verify --show-details

# Enable external integrations
nestgate-cli integration enable --all
```

### Certificate Features
- **Cryptographic Security**: Ed25519 signatures with certificate chains
- **Automatic Validation**: Real-time certificate validity checking
- **Renewal Management**: Automated renewal for multi-year licenses
- **Revocation Support**: Real-time certificate revocation checking
- **Usage Monitoring**: Certificate usage analytics and reporting

